issues.suggested_fix:
Wire the PersonRepository in the template so the PersonService methods can call it. For example, add constructor injection (preferred) or annotate the field for field injection. Example (constructor injection):

public class PersonService {
    private final PersonRepository personRepository;

    public PersonService(PersonRepository personRepository) {
        this.personRepository = personRepository;
    }
    // ...
}

Alternatively, annotate the field with @Autowired:

@Autowired
private PersonRepository personRepository;

Either change will make personRepository available at runtime and align the template with the solution's structure.
